Package MOBLIMA

Class Show

  • java.lang.Object
    • MOBLIMA.Show
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable
    public class Show
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable
    Represents a show entity. This is different from a movie as a show represents when a movie is showed at a cineplex at a given date and time. A movie can have multiple shows.
    Since:
    2019-11-13
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    SS1 Group 2
    See Also:
